|4 |    │ └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR (BROADCAST)|:EX10000|
|5 |    │   └─PX BLOCK ITERATOR           |        |
|6 |    │     └─TABLE FULL SCAN           |t2      |
|7 |    └─PX BLOCK ITERATOR               |        |
|8 |      └─TABLE FULL SCAN               |t1      |
====================================================
